Read the full conventions in `.ai/guidelines/frontend-workflow.md` and
the playbook in `.ai/skills/update-vue-ui/SKILL.md` before changing
behavior.

## Hard rules

- Composition API + `<script setup>` only.
- HTTP via `Nova.request()` — never `import axios`.
- Tailwind utility classes only; no separate Tailwind config.
- Heroicons via inline `<svg>`.
- No new npm runtime dependencies without discussion (every kB ships
  in every consuming app).
- `dist/` is committed on purpose — run `npm run build` and stage
  `dist/` in the same commit as the source change.
- Polling must pause on `document.visibilityState === 'hidden'` and
  the thread must keep using `?after=<lastId>` for delta-only fetches.

