| Concern | File |
|---|---|
| Outer shell | `resources/js/pages/Tool.vue` |
| Tab switcher | `resources/js/components/TopicTabs.vue` |
| Sidebar list | `resources/js/components/ConversationList.vue` |
| Thread + composer | `resources/js/components/ConversationPane.vue` |
| Message bubble | `resources/js/components/MessageBubble.vue` |
| Composer input | `resources/js/components/MessageComposer.vue` |
| Time helpers | `resources/js/lib/time.js` |
